This directory holds configuration files for https://mybinder.org/.

The interactive notebook can be accessed with this link:
https://mybinder.org/v2/gh/calysto/octave_kernel/main?urlpath=/octave_kernel.ipynb

To check out a different version, just replace `main` with the desired
branch/tag name or commit hash.

To use JupyterLab, use:
https://mybinder.org/v2/gh/calysto/ipywidgets/main?urlpath=lab/tree/
